column5: You must complete the quest 'Enemy at the Gate' first.
You must complete the quest 'Breaking Some Eggs' first.
You must complete the quest 'The Root of the Problem' first.
You must complete the quest 'The Way Forward' first.
The way is impassable due to the Undying blockage.
The bridge across is blocked by a thaumaturgical barrier.
You must pierce the hide with the Rapture device.
You need the Sign of Purity to access the Cathedral Rooftop.
You need to find the missing Karui eye to open the gate.
You must defeat Tukohama to unlock the exit.
You must light the Beacon to access the Brine King's Reef.
The bandits have blocked the way. You must find another way around.
You must find a way to clear the Sandstorm to access the Oasis.
You must deliver the ingredients to Sin to access the Beast.
